<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.WindowInfoWayland.Constructor" Title="Constructor method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.WindowInfoWayland">WindowInfoWayland</PageRef> ->
    Constructor
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>WindowInfoWayland</TypeRef> constructor creates a platform binding structure and initializes the inherited <TypeRef>structureSizeInBytes</TypeRef> and type discriminator fields.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[WindowInfoWayland(wl_display* display, wl_surface* surface, const V2UInt32& windowSizeInPixels);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="wl_display*" Name="display">
          The Wayland display.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="wl_surface*" Name="surface">
          The Wayland surface to bind.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="const V2UInt32&amp;" Name="windowSizeInPixels">
          The current drawable window size in pixels.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
